<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277362>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Wings: 1, A. matogrossensis (holotype); 2, A. oiapoquensis (holotype); 3 – 4, A. rafaeli (Brazil: Chácara Arara Azul, USNMENT 00671865, USNMENT 00671867); 5, A. siculigera (holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277362/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.277363>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 12. Female terminalia: 6 – 7, A. matogrossensis (holotype), aculeus and tip, ventral; 8 – 9, A. oiapoquensis (holotype), aculeus and tip, ventral; 10 – 12, A. siculigera (holotype), aculeus, lateral and ventral, and tip, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/277363/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

